102
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:12,112
You are here because Ruifang,
this girl who served us,

103
00:05:12,145 --> 00:05:15,048
she is one of the new heroes,

104
00:05:15,082 --> 00:05:16,884
the new generation heroes...
Right.

105
00:05:16,917 --> 00:05:20,954
That's out to protect
and preserve our food culture.

106
00:05:20,988 --> 00:05:22,148
You know I've been talking about

107
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:24,358
continuity for the longest time.

108
00:05:24,392 --> 00:05:29,196
I mean, I know you want to see
traditional recipes

109
00:05:29,229 --> 00:05:31,832
