155
00:07:17,004 --> 00:07:19,306
Ah, "For Rent:
Cooked Food Stall."

156
00:07:19,339 --> 00:07:20,908
We should do a... do a pop-up.

157
00:07:21,942 --> 00:07:23,176
Get my apron.

