00:26:56,382 --> 00:26:58,450
By ensuring its citizens
are safe,

586
00:26:58,484 --> 00:27:00,787
housed, healthy,
and for the most part

587
00:27:00,820 --> 00:27:02,655
economically successful,

588
00:27:02,689 --> 00:27:04,490
the Singaporean government
has been effective

589
00:27:04,523 --> 00:27:06,659
at keeping the masses
placated enough,

590
00:27:06,693 --> 00:27:09,361
willing to accept curbs
on their freedoms

591
00:27:09,395 --> 00:27:11,030
and civil liberties.

592
00:27:11,063 --> 00:27:15,367
Do you think that
the Singaporean success story

593
00:27:15,401 --> 00:27:19,005
is a rebuke to American
Western values

594
00:27:19,038 --> 00:27:20,306
in some respect?
No, no.

595
00:27:20,339 --> 00:27:21,566
I mean, is free
speech overrated?

596
00:27:21,573 --> 00:27:23,209
I don't think we've succeeded

597
00:27:23,242 --> 00:27:24,944
because of the absence
of free speech.

598
00:27:24,977 --> 00:27:27,006
And to a large extent...
