603
00:27:33,986 --> 00:27:35,287
Asia did not...

604
00:27:35,321 --> 00:27:37,489
It shouldn't work.

605
00:27:37,523 --> 00:27:42,061
It hasn't... it hasn't really
worked like this anywhere else,

606
00:27:42,094 --> 00:27:44,230
and yet it... it works.

